4 cups rice, rinsed
2 fresh tomatoes, chopped
4 red bell peppers, chopped
1 red onion, chopped
1/2 red onion, thinly sliced
3 habaneros
3 tbsp tomato paste
4 cloves garlic

Seasoning Blend
1 tsp curry powder
1/2 teaspoon thyme
4 seasoning cubes
1/2 tsp nutmeg
1/2 tbsp pepper
1/4 tsp white pepper
3 bay leaves
Salt to taste

STEPS

Rinse rice
Puree
    tomatoes
    peppers
    onion
    garlic
    habaneros
Saut√© sliced onion until golden
Add tomato paste
Fry until dark
Add puree
Fry until thickened and bubbling
Add 2C water
Add seasoning
Bring to a simmer
Add rice
Mix well
Add Bay Leaves
Cover
Reduce to low
Cook for 45min